    public static enum SkyRenderElement.FAST_LINES
extends java.lang.Enum<SkyRenderElement.FAST_LINES>
    The set of options to draw fast lines for better performance.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      GRID_AND_CONSTELLATIONS

      NONE
      Never use fast mode.
      ONLY_GRID
      Use fast line rendering for grid.
